Introduction

Um Jiwon is a South Korean trainee under H1GHR MUSIC. She is a member of the agency's upcoming girl group along three others I-LAND2: N/a contestants.

In 2024, Um Jiwon was a contestant on Mnet's survival show I-LAND2: N/a, where she was sadly eliminated in episode 7. At that time, she was a trainee under WAKEONE.
